[{"text": "<!-- Page 1 -->", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "Decision", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "At its 1615th meeting, on 15 December 1971, the Council decided to invite the representative of Ceylon to participate, without vote, in the discussion of the question.", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "Resolution 307 (1971)", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "of 21 December 1971", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "The Security Council,", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "Having discussed the grave situation in the subcontinent, which remains a threat to international peace and security,", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "Noting General Assembly resolution 2793 (XXVI) of 7 December 1971,", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "Noting the reply of the Government of Pakistan on 9 December 1971,83", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "Noting the reply of the Government of India on 12 December 1971,84", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "Having heard the statements of the Deputy Prime Minister of Pakistan85 and the Foreign Minister of India,86", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "Noting further the statement made at the 1616th meeting of the Security Council by the Foreign Minister of India containing a unilateral declaration of a cease-fire in the western theatre,", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "Noting Pakistan’s agreement to the cease-fire in the western theatre with effect from 17 December 1971,87", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "Noting that consequently a cease-fire and a cessation of hostilities prevail,", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "1. Demands that a durable cease-fire and cessation of all hostilities in all areas of conflict be strictly observed and remain in effect until withdrawals take place, as soon as practicable, of all armed forces to their respective territories and to positions which fully respect the cease-fire line in Jammu and Kashmir supervised by the United Nations Military Observer Group in India and Pakistan;", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "2. Calls upon all Member States to refrain from any action which may aggravate the situation in the subcontinent or endanger international peace;", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "3. Calls upon all those concerned to take all measures necessary to preserve human life and for the observance of the Geneva Conventions of 194958 and to apply in full their provisions as regards the protection of the wounded and sick, prisoners of war and civilian population;", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "4. Calls for international assistance in the relief of suffering and the rehabilitation of refugees and their return in safety and dignity to their homes, and for full co-operation with the Secretary-General to that effect;", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "5. Authorizes the Secretary-General to appoint if necessary a special representative to lend his good offices for the solution of humanitarian problems;", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "6. Requests the Secretary-General to keep the Council informed without delay on developments relating to the implementation of the present resolution;", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "7. Decides to remain seized of the matter and to keep it under active consideration.", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "Adopted at the 1621st meeting by 13 votes to none, with 2 abstentions (Poland, Union of Soviet Socialist Republics).", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "---", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "| Footnotes |", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "|-----------|", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "| 83 See Official Records of the Security Council, Twenty-sixth Year, Supplement for October, November and December 1971, document S/10440. |", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "| 84 Ibid., document S/10445. |", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "| 85 Ibid., Twenty-sixth Year, 1614th meeting. |", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "| 86 Ibid., 1613th meeting. |", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "| 87 Ibid., 1621st meeting. |", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "| 88 United Nations, Treaty Series, vol. 75 (1950), Nos. 970-973. |", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "---", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "QUESTION CONCERNING THE ISLANDS OF ABU MUSA, THE GREATER TUNB AND THE LESSER TUNB", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "Decisions", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "At its 1610th meeting, on 9 December 1971, the Council decided to invite the representatives of Iraq, Iran, Algeria, the Libyan Arab Republic, the People’s Democratic Republic of Yemen, Kuwait and the United Arab Emirates to participate, without vote, in the discussion of the item entitled “Letter dated 3 December 1971 from the Permanent Representatives of Algeria, Iraq, the Libyan Arab Republic and the People’s Democratic Republic of Yemen to the United Nations addressed to the President of the Security Council (S/10409)”.59", "type": "frontmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": 